{"lemma":"ضَعَة","slug":"ضَعَة","root":"#.ض.ع","root_slug":"_-ض-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ض-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n25860","n44633"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B6%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n25860","headword_ar":"ضَعَةٌ","root":"DEw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaEowN","text_ar":"ضَعْوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaEawN","text_ar":"ضَعَوٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (accord. to different copies of the S,) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"being a substitute [for the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"], because of the form of its pl. [and of the rel. n.]; or, as some say, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a substitute for an initial"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":", and it is mentioned also in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wDE","text_ar":"وضع"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A species of tree,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the desert:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or it is ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a plant"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"species of panic grass called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vumaAm","text_ar":"ثُمَام"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) accord. to Az,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a species of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vumaAm","text_ar":"ثُمَام"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vm","text_ar":"ثم"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"another plant:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and some pronounce it"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DiEapN","text_ar":"ضِعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but this is in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHasab","text_ar":"الحَسَب"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or grounds of pretension to respect &c.], and does not belong to the present art.: (TA:) the pl. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DaEawaAtN","text_ar":"ضَعَوَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, TA.) [Golius says, on the authority of Meyd, that it also signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"reed of which writing-reeds are made."},{"kind":"text","text":"]"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n44633","headword_ar":"ضَِعَةٌ","root":"wDE","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"perhaps an inf. n. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waDaEato","text_ar":"وَضَعَتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning “ she brought forth: ” see 1, third sentence, in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qrA^","text_ar":"قرا"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}